name: SUPERVOID
description:
DISCLAIMER: This game might not be suitable for people with photosensitive epilepsy.

SUPERVOID is a fast-paced arcade runner with colourful minimalist visuals and a synthwave soundtrack.

Features

  • 9 levels
  • Leaderboards
  • Unlockable colour themes
  • Stats for each level
  • Music by DOS-88
  • Simple 2-button play - Play with keyboard or controller
